caption:
It’s @fwecanada’s Gala time! Calling all champions of women entrepreneurs. 

Register now to attend and vote live at @fwecanada's The Odlum Brown FWE Gala: Pitch for the Purse Finale 5pm PST on Feb 25th, 2021! Watch 3 amazing pitches and vote to decide the Winner of the $50,000 grand prize. 

Since the pandemic started, the number of women entrepreneurs seeking help from @fwecanada has skyrocketed, resulting in @fwecanada helping over 5,000 women entrepreneurs in the last 10 months alone. Help us raise money to fund the amazing education and mentorship that @fwecanada provides.

Registration is free. RSVP to vote and donate now at fwe.ca/pitch-for-the-purse 

#pitchforthepurse #FWE #wildlysuccessful
